		{
			dependencies: ["VL01000000000009"]
			description: ["Stem cells are the biological foundation of wetware circuit boards. Grow them in a cell incubator at tightly controlled atmospheric conditions—they die if temperature deviates by more than half a degree. The colony takes time to establish. Start it now, before you need it."]
