		}
		{
			dependencies: ["EH01000000000001"]
			description: ["The wetware circuit board is a hybrid substrate: a standard PCB printed with bio-conductive pathways, then seeded with living stem cell culture. The cells grow into the pathways and form synaptic connections that no silicon circuit can replicate. Handle carefully—the culture is still alive."]
