			description: ["Soul cultivation, Botania mana, Blood Magic life points, and GTCEu electrical engineering—four independent systems with nothing in common except that your hands built them all. The Way of the Soul recognizes this as mastery, not coincidence. Something shifts in the fabric between worlds."]
